How to make this face mask

Ingredients:- 

1) honey
2) besan
3) coffee
4) haldi
5) dahi

MIX EVERYTHING AND APPLY THIS MASK ON YOUR FACE AND WAIT UNTIL IT DRY... AFTER DRYING JUST TAKE COLD WATER AND WASH IT OFF

The combination of coffee with besan, haldi, honey, and dahi yields a face pack that not only brightens the skin but also provides exfoliating and moisturizing benefits. Coffee is known to possess strong antioxidant properties, which aids in reducing suntan, as well as in enhancing skin complexion owing to besan's exfoliating properties. Some sources describe the turmeric possessing anti-inflammatory capabilities, assisting with dark spots and pigmentation. The soothing benefits of honey, in addition to dahi's (yogurt) lactic acid content that helps eliminate dead skin cells, aids in getting a fresh, radiant complexion, giving skin that Added Glow.
